data.description: Beautiful single story home with a 4 car garage and casita set in 2 wooded acres. Property is fully fenced with electric gate access, private well and several young fruit trees. Pellet stove and radiant floor heating throughout main home and attached 3 car garage. Vaulted tongue and groove ceiling and large kitchen area. 2022: New stainless steel matching fridge, dishwasher, microwave, range, blinds, washer/dryer all convey. Attached 3 car garage is fully insulated. 2017: carpeting, tankless water heater and septic were replaced. 2001: metal roof. Fresh paint throughout home and casita. Casita has baseboard heating, kitchenette, full bath and loft bedroom potential + newer window A/C. Perfect for revenue or multigenerational living.
